---
title: Duck Pie with a Potato and Cheese Topping
description: We love a good Duck Pie and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/duck-pie-7b9fdfb7-2a4c2d28.jpg
